Package edu.umd.cloud9.example.bfs

Class Summary
BFSNode Representation of a graph node for parallel breadth-first search.
EncodeBFSGraph Tool for taking a plain-text encoding of a directed graph and building corresponding Hadoop structures for running parallel breadth-first search.
FindNodeAtDistance Tool for extracting nodes that are a particular distance from the source node.
FindReachableNodes Tool for extracting nodes that are reachable from the source node.
IterateBFS Tool for running one iteration of parallel breadth-first search.
